<li><a href="/wiki/Fichier:Order_of_Pakistan.png" class="image"><img alt="Order of Pakistan.png" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e2/Order_of_Pakistan.png/50px-Order_of_Pakistan.png" decoding="async" width="50" height="14" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e2/Order_of_Pakistan.png/75px-Order_of_Pakistan.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e2/Order_of_Pakistan.png/100px-Order_of_Pakistan.png 2x" data-file-width="106" data-file-height="30" /></a> Membre de l'ordre de <a href="/w/index.php?title=Nishan-e-Pakistan&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Nishan-e-Pakistan (page inexistante)">Nishan-e-Pakistan</a>&#160;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nishan-e-Pakistan" class="extiw" title="en:Nishan-e-Pakistan"><span class="indicateur-langue" title="Équivalent de l’article «&#160;Nishan-e-Pakistan&#160;» en anglais">(en)</span></a> (Pakistan, 1992).</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Fichier:LUX_Order_of_Adolphe_Nassau_Grand_Cross_BAR.png" class="image" title="LUX Order of Adolphe Nassau Grand Cross BAR"><img alt="LUX Order of Adolphe Nassau Grand Cross BAR" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/3d/LUX_Order_of_Adolphe_Nassau_Grand_Cross_BAR.png/50px-LUX_Order_of_Adolphe_Nassau_Grand_Cross_BAR.png" decoding="async" width="50" height="14" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/3d/LUX_Order_of_Adolphe_Nassau_Grand_Cross_BAR.png/75px-LUX_Order_of_Adolphe_Nassau_Grand_Cross_BAR.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/3d/LUX_Order_of_Adolphe_Nassau_Grand_Cross_BAR.png/100px-LUX_Order_of_Adolphe_Nassau_Grand_Cross_BAR.png 2x" data-file-width="212" data-file-height="59" /></a> Grand-croix de l'<a href="/wiki/Ordre_d%27Adolphe_de_Nassau" title="Ordre d&#39;Adolphe de Nassau">ordre d'Adolphe de Nassau</a> (Pays-Bas, 1999).</li>
