i/Principes_de_Sullivan" title="Principes de Sullivan">Principes de Sullivan</a></span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/South_African_Defence_Force" title="South African Defence Force">SADF</a></span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Police_sud-africaine" title="Police sud-africaine">SAP</a></span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Supplice_du_pneu" title="Supplice du pneu">Supplice du pneu</a></span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Test_du_crayon" title="Test du crayon">Test du crayon</a></span></td>
