hav Karve (page inexistante)">Dhondo Keshav Karve</a>&#160;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dhondo_Keshav_Karve" class="extiw" title="en:Dhondo Keshav Karve"><span class="indicateur-langue" title="Équivalent de l’article «&#160;Dhondo Keshav Karve&#160;» en anglais">(en)</span></a> (1958)</span></td>
